<bibRefCitation id="F11753CC9A36FFC2FC30FECBDBB1BB56" author="STEURBAUT E." box="[1003,1164,305,329]" pageId="39" pageNumber="348" pagination="247 - 277" refId="ref43706" refString="STEURBAUT E. 2011. - New calcareous nannofossil taxa from the Ypresian (Early Eocene) of the North Sea Basin and the Turan Platform in West Kazakhstan. Bulletin de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, Sciences de la Terre 81: 247 - 277." type="journal article" year="2011">Steurbaut, 2011</bibRefCitation>
